%% Diagram: Inline cache state progression on a single property load
%% Type: stateDiagram-v2
stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR
    [*] --> Uninitialized: first call
    Uninitialized --> Monomorphic: 1 shape seen<br/>direct memory load
    Monomorphic --> Polymorphic: 2-4 shapes<br/>small lookup table
    Polymorphic --> Megamorphic: 5+ shapes<br/>fall back to runtime lookup
    Megamorphic --> [*]: stays megamorphic<br/>(IC frozen for the site)

    note right of Monomorphic
        Fastest path:
        load at cached offset
    end note
    note right of Megamorphic
        Slow path:
        no caching, full property lookup
    end note
